 2023 年黑胶唱片销量增长近 15% https://www.nme.com/news/music/vinyl-sales-up-nearly-15-per-cent-in-2023-3509810?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=vinyl-sales-up-nearly-15- 2023 年百分比Liberty DunworthThu, 05 Oct 2023 10:14:48 +0000 Music NewsNewsVinyl https://www.nme.com/?p=3509810 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑胶唱片 库存照片" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)、Blur 和拉娜·德雷 (Lana Del Rey) 的专辑位列最畅销专辑之列</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>率先报道了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vinyl-sales-up-nearly-15-per-cent-in-2023-3509810">2023 年黑胶唱片销量将增长近 15% 的</a>消息。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑胶唱片 库存照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一份新报告显示，2023 年前 9 个月黑胶唱片销量同比飙升近 15%。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/whats-causing-the-vinyl-delay-adele-is-not-the-problem-say-music-industry-insiders-3094213">是什么导致黑胶唱片延迟？音乐业内人士表示：“阿黛尔不是问题”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该统计数据是从 BPI（通过<a href="https://www.musicweek.com/labels/read/vinyl-sales-surge-13-2-in-2023-ahead-of-black-friday-and-blockbuster-q4/088617" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>MusicWeek</em></a> ）收集的，并强调从今年年初到 9 月底，黑胶唱片销量为 3,952,262 张——自 2022 年以来大约增长了 13.2%。</p><p>根据该报告，第三季度的三个月内这一增幅更​​大，黑胶唱片销量达到 1,237,620 张；这一数字比上年增长了15.1%。</p><p>到目前为止，主要推动黑胶唱片销售复苏的艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">拉娜·德雷 (Lana Del Rey)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift</a> )、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a>和凯莉·米洛<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kylie-minogue">(Kylie Minogue</a> )，他们自今年年初以来都发行了新的密纹唱片。</p><p>到目前为止，Lana Del Rey 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lana-del-rey-did-you-know-that-theres-a-tunnel-under-ocean-blvd-review-3415497">Did You Know That There&#39;s A Tunnel Under Ocean Blvd</a> 》仍然是今年销量最大的黑胶唱片——自 3 月份发行以来，该格式已售出 33,568 张。其次是泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的《Speak Now (Taylor&#39;s Version)》，这是第三季度最畅销的黑胶唱片，销量达到 29,649 张。</p><p>排名第三的是英国流行音乐偶像 Blur，其第九张录音室专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blur-the-ballad-of-darren-review-lyrics-tracklist-3470424">The Ballad Of Darren</a> 》已售出 26,894 张，凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue) 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kylie-minogue-tension-review-lyrics-tracklist-3501195">Tension</a> 》也紧随其后，自上个月发行以来已售出 19,160 张。 </p><figure id="attachment_3509821" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3509821" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3509821" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在 2023 年 The Eras 巡演期间表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Taylor-Swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3509821" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在 2023 年 The Eras 巡演期间表演。图片来源：Allen J. Schaben/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>其他为黑胶唱片销量铺平道路的专辑包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-rodrigo-guts-album-review-vampire-3493907">Guts</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wham">《Wham!》</a>的《单身者：天堂边缘的回声》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lewis-capaldi">刘易斯·卡帕尔迪</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lewis-capaldi-broken-by-desire-to-be-heavenly-sent-review-3444656">被天堂派遣的渴望所破碎</a>》。</p><p>更重要的是，这一数字预计将在 2023 年剩余时间内大幅上升， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">Take That</a> （“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/take-that-return-announce-new-album-and-announce-massive-uk-and-ireland-stadium-tour-pre-order-buy-tickets-3502377">This Life</a> ”）和 Taylor Swift（“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/streams-of-taylor-swifts-1989-double-after-re-recording-announcement-3483064">1989（泰勒版）</a> ”）的专辑仍将发行。另一位今年将在数字上留下巨大印记的艺术家是摇滚<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">偶像滚石乐队</a>，他们将于 10 月 20 日分享“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-confirm-new-album-hackney-diamonds-and-single-angry-3494112">Hackney Diamonds</a> ”——他们 18 年来的第一张原创音乐新专辑。</p><p>随着黑色星期五——唱片店日的姊妹活动——即将到来（11 月 24 日），这一数字还将进一步增加。此次活动将为 90 多位艺术家发行限量版黑胶唱片，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">Joni Mitchell</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-doors">The Doors</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/post-malone">Post Malone</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3509823" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3509823" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3509823" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270.jpg" alt="音乐黑胶唱片收藏复古复古风格 图库照片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vinyl-stock-photo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3509823" class="wp-caption-text">音乐黑胶唱片收藏复古复古风格 – 图库照片。图片来源：凯莉·鲍登/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>据<em>《音乐周刊》</em>报道，2023 年 CD 销量同比下降 6.3%，实体销量整体下降 0.5%。毫不奇怪，流媒体仍然是音乐消费的主要方式，占据了 88.5% 的市场份额。</p><p>在其他乙烯基新闻中，早在 8 月份就有报道称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scotlands-first-ever-vinyl-pressing-plant-is-under-construction-3487364">苏格兰第一家乙烯基压制工厂正在建设中，预计将于今年晚些时候开业</a>。</p><p> Seabass Vinyl 是 David 和 Dominique Harvey 的家族企业，将于本月晚些时候在爱丁堡郊外的东洛锡安开业。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>率先报道了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vinyl-sales-up-nearly-15-per-cent-in-2023-3509810">2023 年黑胶唱片销量将增长近 15% 的</a>消息。</p> ;
