深情的《As It Was》。她还演奏了她的 2023 年舞池单曲“Little Things”。您可以在下面的视频中观看这两场表演。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Jorja Smith - As It Was（Harry Styles 封面）在现场休息室" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/v3I92UZZLEw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Jorja Smith - 现场休息室里的小事" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VEKnD8KRwXc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>本周早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-olivia-rodrigo-cover-noah-kahans-stick-season-bbc-radio-1-live-lounge-3508478">Olivia Rodrigo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-troye-sivan-cover-billie-eilishs-what-was-i-made-for-in-bbc-radio-1s-live-lounge-3508521">Troye Sivan</a>参加了 Live Lounge Month 2023，他们分别翻唱了 Noah Kahan 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 。其他尚未在该剧中演出的演员包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madison-beer">麦迪逊·比尔 (Madison Beer)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/royal-blood">皇家血统</a>(Royal Blood)、霍莉·亨伯斯通 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone)</a> 、永布鲁德 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">Yungblud)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/usher">亚瑟小子 (Usher</a> )。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jorja-smith-falling-or-flying-review-rb-star-finds-a-joyful-complex-sound-3505079">对史密斯新专辑的四星评论</a>中写道：“《Falling or Flying》是她注定要做的唱片，她只需要让自己到达那里。”</p><p>史密斯此前解释说，唱片中的歌曲“涉及分手、与朋友的关系、与老朋友的关系以及与自己的关系”。</p><p> “这肯定与很多关系有关，但我写的每首歌我都可以唱给自己听，”她补充道。 “这是我第一次把我现在可以连接的东西放在那里。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-jorja-smith-cover-harry-styles-as-it-was-for-live-lounge-month-3509691">观看 Jorja Smith 为 Live Loung